{"tid":379070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民的眼睛是雪亮的。長官，妳看得懂嗎？","createTime":"2017-08-29T03:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T04:28:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be7cb5215ce525c05f08e743e25633d8aae1a277","tid":379070,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:41:28.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒母致函林鄭　<br />\n「苛政峻法豈能阻青年尋公義」<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170829/large/a0602a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170829%2Flarge%2Fa0602a.gif&h=c46a2400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃之鋒因政府就衝擊公民廣場案覆核刑期而被判入獄，其母（右圖）昨寫公開信予特首林鄭月娥。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「雙學三子」因政府就衝擊公民廣場案覆核刑期而被判入獄，一向低調的黃之鋒母親日前撰寫公開信予特首林鄭月娥，質疑林鄭是否真的理解雙學三子父母的心情，「為何追究的對象不是擲下87枚催淚彈、傷盡港人心的發號施令者？」<br />\n林鄭早前開腔談及雙學三子被判囚時，提到作為「兩個20幾歲仔」的媽媽，理解雙學三子母親的心情。惟黃母在《香港01》周報撰寫《黃之鋒母致特首書》，反問林鄭是否真的理解雙學三子母親的心情，斥掌權者選擇性執法及政治迫害，已引起社會極大迴響，「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人民的眼睛是雪亮的。長官，妳看得懂嗎？</span>」本報昨向特首辦查詢，截稿前未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n對兒子擇善固執感欣慰<br />\n<br />\n黃母指，林鄭自詡於火紅的年代參與過社運，卻又安然全身而退入職政府，以至位極特區之首，「妳理解孩子們的所作所為，不過是爬欄進入原為『門常開』變『門要關』的『公民廣場』，卻被加罪等同『暴力』、『暴動』，要被重審追加刑期至6至8個月？」黃母更質疑，爬欄之舉竟以當時未發生的雨傘運動規模和影響去定罪，「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沒有87枚催淚彈，就沒有雨傘運動，為何追究的對象不是擲下87枚催淚彈、傷盡港人心的發號施令者？</span>」<br />\n<br />\n黃母又指，黃之鋒就讀直資中學，大可升讀英美學府，對香港困境置身事外，但兒子願以微小的力量守護香港，反問林鄭：「身為母親，妳可理解我對兒子能夠『擇善而固執之』的欣慰？」黃母於信末強調，不會讓政府選擇性檢控及執法，隨時隨地搬龍門，把良心公義之士的反對聲音滅聲，葬送整整一代年輕人的未來，「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">苛政峻法，豈能鎖得住香港年輕一代對公義民權的追求？</span>」<br />\n<br />\n■記者李詠希"},{"pid":"01d7d12d75bc05caba8e6051333758945b652480","tid":379070,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818be6b248b2ebb2e38ec1ac358d06c1768f3d8d","tid":379070,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"「身為母親，妳可理解我對兒子能夠『擇善而固執之』的欣慰？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efe007f043f715f2c25d439358e56036e5a5573","tid":379070,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b1be1378f620a8389541b7e0a27c44075a572e","tid":379070,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:43:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20135653&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20135653%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170829&d=CBxb65HEqgX8oStXjL8iVACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7e38b1d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20135653%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170829&h=28f639aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20135653&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170829</a>"},{"pid":"f26aecc426b66dd3312ef9fc8d0973c2d9f7ba90","tid":379070,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"遺憾既係人民大都有視障"},{"pid":"8150778563fa9719ba5ec332aa8a4c28663cfeff","tid":379070,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遺憾既係人民大都有視障</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}